snippet.title: Tom Clancy’s Rainbow Six Siege – Neon Dawn: Gameplay and Tips
snippet.description:
Discover Aruni, the new Operator joining team Rainbow and her abilities, as well as the brand-new Skryscraper map with everything that the season is bringing to the game.


Learn more: http://www.rainbow6.com/neondawn
